structure.unit: LIQUEFIED PETROLEUM GAS AND OTHER FLAMMABLE LIQUIDS

law.text: All moneys collected under the provisions of KRS 234.100 to 234.160 shall be paid into the State Treasury and credited to a trust and agency fund to be used by the Department of Housing, Buildings and Construction solely for the administration and enforcement of KRS 234.100 to 234.160 and 234.990.
law.history: Amended 2010 Ky. Acts ch. 24, sec. 499, effective July 15, 2010. -- Amended 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 117, sec. 27, effective July 1, 1978. -- Amended 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 74, Art. V, sec. 20. -- Amended 1960 Ky. Acts ch. 138, sec. 11, effective June 16, 1960. -- Created 1952 Ky. Acts ch. 25, sec. 7.
